    "description": "PhonePe South Asia Partners has an exciting opening for a Backend Developer at our Srinagar office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout PhonePe South Asia Partners:\nPhonePe South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Srinagar, Jammu & Kashmir, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with PhonePe South Asia Partners!",
